From: H. Peter Anvin <hpa@linux.intel.com>
Subject: x86, mwait: Move mwait constants to a common header file
References: fate#311818,fate#311942
Patch-Mainline: yes
Git-commit: 0d377ee9506d73b26852a9f2a03e87412532a83a


Signed-off-by: Thomas Renninger <trenn@suse.de>

upstream: bc83cccc761953f878088cdfa682de0970b5561f

